# 5 Read_Structure

This section we will going into implementation of
structures in C/C++ programming language.

By structure's variable as well as pointer

-- The nature of structure, is some adjacent memory locations, which is addressed by add the offset to the base address.

-----------------------------------
Some fun facts as shown in the C++ source code file

1.  Allocation of non-aligned or not in accordance with 32-bit boundary. --Auto alignment done by Compiler

2.  The allocation of CPU Registers while operating structures. -- Not only use EAX and ECX, but also uses EDX


